  "title": "A Little Something for the Ducks",
  "description": "A 78 year-old woman. A 79 year-old man. A mallard named Nellie. A bag full of bread crusts. The big question: will they or won’t they feed the ducks? Winner of Outstanding Technical, Performance, Director, and Production at the ADFA Provincials 2024. Also on the bill, Something’s Wrong by G.A. Northrup.",
